{"tid":1409374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"狗乸又出黎講野","createTime":"2019-08-04T20:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T21:24:12.000Z","uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"92d20c97e605b9e456286e2af8a14646d2091b7a","tid":1409374,"uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:47:46.000Z","msg":"立場live"},{"pid":"fa4932885682db4190ac29c083de1fc1fc8a6e07","tid":1409374,"uid":4484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:48:29.000Z","msg":"又咪講個啲廢話"},{"pid":"7e81d560c38bb8afcc8be55dfe9f275b5b0faddc","tid":1409374,"uid":198035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:48:32.000Z","msg":"咪又係講廢話"},{"pid":"c191e79a4752df51cfab97cba006c1830b4a4880","tid":1409374,"uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:48:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/490556701503303/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F490556701503303%2F&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QoRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=6edde978\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/490556701503303/</a>"},{"pid":"dfd8e18dc390503e6ebf296eefa155428b435097","tid":1409374,"uid":150742,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:48:42.000Z","msg":"[請廣傳] FORWARDED FROM TELEGRAM<br />\n朋友既朋友 警隊臨床心理學家指出唔少警察<br />\n長期聽到針對警察示威口號產生幻聽、躁鬱、最嚴重會患上抑鬱等<br />\n<br />\n若示威者同警察距離非常近既時候, 利用群眾優勢<br />\n不要說「黑警，可恥」, 試著說「黑社會」,這種標籤化令警察內心會感自愧, 壓力倍僧, 行為自動檢點<br />\n<br />\n進一步造成心理創傷口號，不要說「香港警察，知法犯法」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">試著說「不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意」</span>此口號出自警察誓言, 當有人不斷叫出此口號，警察會回憶畢業既誓言，開始對自己身份認同產生懷疑同混淆, 精神疲乏, 有部份警察雙眼通紅、帶有淚光<br />\n<br />\n終極核彈級口號, 有機會造成永久心理創傷, 相信好快用得「殺人兇手」 當事實真的發生，不論兇手有沒有殺人，身處同一個群體，都變成兇手, <br />\n不單面對極大壓力而崩塌, 伴隨的是恐懼、抑鬱, 更重要是這種負面情緒會災難性地爆發傳遍整個群體"},{"pid":"a4fc224e818087cf48497327f1d45cd776019587","tid":1409374,"uid":198035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:48:53.000Z","msg":"叫佢回應下警署開槍"},{"pid":"d6e2fd1fac56eda31610fbde37610a18fef40372","tid":1409374,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:49:49.000Z","msg":"越演越烈越演越烈越演越烈"},{"pid":"953f60a404351dda73658ce492e1a1ac20de565d","tid":1409374,"uid":200493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然我都知佢係錄音機 不過嬲到訓唔到 <br />\n入黎屌下 發洩下先<br />\n聽日見各位"},{"pid":"ccaf0bdcb59b5aea51a6bb05f782f71dbe91b60f","tid":1409374,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:50:16.000Z","msg":"越演越烈"},{"pid":"01af3dabbe75e8a14168798bc4fdf9dfb63ebea9","tid":1409374,"uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:52:05.000Z","msg":"根本你狗就係冇撚用"},{"pid":"7ba901135a4d6299735bdafc44545868a17faa08","tid":1409374,"uid":8918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:52:29.000Z","msg":"希望傳媒朋友杯葛黑警記者會, 杯葛完全冇合法性既機構"},{"pid":"28cc57028327095180622f9f6fae3a8148890095","tid":1409374,"uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:52:43.000Z","msg":"冇警告開槍啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"11f82b74bc3b3ac1bc405a1db1ef661926807a17","tid":1409374,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:52:53.000Z","msg":"人地問你點解開槍呀"},{"pid":"798f0e180aa781bdc8f43e969e46aa26746a440a","tid":1409374,"uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:53:07.000Z","msg":"交代各區啊"},{"pid":"659f57c6571d67359abf23d7f522e63a8ad4cc9d","tid":1409374,"uid":40439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:53:25.000Z","msg":"觀塘警署暗殺示威者！"},{"pid":"a17c57a1a3a13690b901939c53cdaf32243d6a9e","tid":1409374,"uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:53:31.000Z","msg":"你冇警告開槍啊"},{"pid":"be5e54abbbab4dae3d6fd48b7